                <h1>Professor Schewel reflects on activist career and potential mayoral run</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/6cf0a25a-9151-4a8e-a58c-4acad4bc7858.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Steve&#x20;Schewel&#x20;has&amp;nbsp&#x3B;served&#x20;on&#x20;the&#x20;Durham&#x20;Public&#x20;Schools&#x2019;&#x20;Board&#x20;of&#x20;Education&#x20;and&#x20;the&#x20;Durham&#x20;City&#x20;Council.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Steve Schewel has&nbsp;served on the Durham Public Schools’ Board of Education and the Durham City Council.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/neelesh-moorthy">Neelesh Moorthy</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">June 6, 2016 | 12:02am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2016/06/professor-schewel-reflects-on-activist-career-and-potential-mayoral-run" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
